 mills, tube presses, and other. The company also provides various systems related to hydraulic equipment for the automobile industry, and cabin-tilting systems to truck manufacturers, as well as undertakes various subcontract and reconditioning works for medium and heavy machineries in heavy engineering, automobile, aeronautical, defense, space industries, and other. In addition, it offers erection/assembly of structures, hydraulics, and control systems services. Further, the company is involved in developing, holding, and letting out real estate properties, as well as trading in and marketing various types of machinery and spares. Alfred Herbert (India) Limited was incorporated in 1919 and is based in Kolkata, India."}}